# Market Intelligence Engine V2 — Walkthrough

## Overview

Upgraded MIYAR's market intelligence layer from a simple scrape-and-insert pipeline to a self-maintaining, self-evolving intelligence engine. The upgrade spans **8 modules** across 3 phases.

---

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Scheduler / API Call"] --> B["Orchestrator V2"]
    B --> C{"findExistingRecord?"}
    C -->|"Found"| D["updateExistingRecord"]
    C -->|"Not Found"| E["createEvidenceRecord"]
    D --> F["detectPriceChange"]
    E --> F
    B --> G["Data Quality Validator"]
    G --> H{"Outlier?"}
    H -->|"Yes"| I["Flag + Reduce Confidence"]
    H -->|"No"| J["Pass Through"]
    
    K["Freshness Monitor"] --> L{"Stale Sources?"}
    L -->|"Yes"| A
    
    M["Source Discovery AI"] --> N["Candidate Sources"]
    N --> O["Admin Review"]
    O --> A
    
    P["Design Trend Extractor"] --> Q["designTrends Table"]
    R["Developer Intel Extractor"] --> S["evidence_records"]
    T["Data Verifier"] --> U["Verification Report"]
```

---

